data.eml:eml: New erythroneurine leafhopper species from the Australian realm (Hemiptera: Cicadellidae: Typhlocybinae)

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Cao, Yanghui, Dmitriev, Dmitry A., Dietrich, Christopher H., Zhang, Yalin (2019): New erythroneurine leafhopper species from the Australian realm (Hemiptera: Cicadellidae: Typhlocybinae). Zootaxa 4671 (2): 251-258, DOI: https://doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.4671.2.5
